{
  "description": "A long-exposure nighttime photograph showcases a vibrant fireworks display over a city skyline and a bridge spanning a dark body of water. The fireworks burst in shades of white, gold, and red, illuminating the sky above the city. The city itself is a tapestry of lights, with buildings of varying heights and architectural styles. A long, illuminated bridge with numerous support pillars stretches across the water, leading towards the cityscape. The water is dark and reflective, with a few scattered red and white navigation lights visible.  The bridge appears modern and sleek, contrasting with the more traditional architecture of the city. There is a soft haze or fog hanging over the water, adding to the atmospheric effect.",
